Introduced Version
HOUSE BILL No. 1206
_____
DIGEST OF INTRODUCED BILL
Citations Affected: IC 36-1-12-4.
Synopsis: Local public work project bidding. Provides additional
considerations that a local public works board may consider in
determining the lowest responsible and responsive bidder for a public
work project costing at least $300,000.
Effective: July 1, 2026.
Olthoff, Karickhoff
January 5, 2026, read first time and referred to Committee on Employment, Labor and
Pensions.
2026 IN 1206—LS 6783/DI 137

Introduced
Second Regular Session of the 124th General Assembly (2026)
PRINTING CODE. Amendments: Whenever an existing statute (or a section of the Indiana
